Class GameOverScreen

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent

javafx.scene.layout.Pane
com.example.demo.GameOverScreen
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class GameOverScreen extends javafx.scene.layout.Pane
This class creates the game over screen that is displayed when the player loses the game. It contains a background image, a game over image, a retry button and a quit button. The retry button restarts the game and the quit button closes the game.
